HEADWORD: Setness
<hw>Set"ness</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality or state
of being set; formality; obstinacy.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧The starched
<xex>setness</xex> of a sententious writer.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>R.
